        "contentType": "raw",
        "rawContentType": "application/json",
        "body": "={{ JSON.stringify({\n  model: \"phi3:mini\",\n  prompt: `Act as a senior cybersecurity threat analyst.\n\nReturn EXACTLY:\n\nWhat Happened:\n- ...\n\nWhy It Matters:\n- ...\n\nWhat To Do:\n- ...\n- ...\n\nFocus on actionable guidance.\nDo not repeat the article.\nInclude title as header and the date.\n\nTitle:\n${$json.title}\nDate:\n${$json.date}\nArticle:\n${$json.content}`,\n  stream: false,\n  options: {\n\tnum_predict: 500,\n\ttemperature: 0.2\n  }\n}) }}\n\n",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 600000
        }
      },
